resources.string:
You can import words from a file, it can be also structured in a simpler hierarchy.
Words with same translate are separated by a backward slash '\'.
Write the file for import in the following format:
name of a chapter
{
a word;its translate
another word;translate
subchapter's name
{
…
}
another subchapter
{
…
}
word 1\word 2;their translate
}
